    <svcsubproc>
        <title>Splitter Cylinder Assembly</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Cut lockwire and remove the lockscrew from the shift yoke (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13018a9">Figure 109</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13018a9" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13018a9" filename="../figg13/G13018a9.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 109. Remove Lockscrew From Shift Yoke</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the bolts from the splitter cylinder cover and remove the splitter cylinder cover and
                gasket (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13018b0">Figure 110</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13018b0" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13018b0" filename="../figg13/G13018b0.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 110. Remove Bolts From Splitter Cylinder Cover</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">If necessary, remove the plug in the bottom bore of the cover and remove the insert valve (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13018b1">Figure 111</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13018b1" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13018b1" filename="../figg13/G13018b1.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 111. Remove Plug in Cover Bottom Bore and Remove Insert Valve</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the yoke bar from the cylinder housing bore (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13018b2">Figure 112</hotlnk>). If necessary, remove the O-ring from the piston O.D. (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13018b2">inset, Figure 112</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13018b2" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13018b2" filename="../figg13/G13018b2.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 112. Remove Yoke Bar and O-Ring</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the splitter cylinder housing and gasket from the auxiliary housing (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13018b3">Figure 113</hotlnk>). If necessary, remove the small O-ring from the cylinder
                housing bore (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13018b3">inset, Figure 113</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13018b3" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13018b3" filename="../figg13/G13018b3.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 113. Remove Splitter Cylinder Housing, Gasket, and Small O-Ring</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
    </svcsubproc>
